text: KEPT-LP is a low power radio station broadcasting from Hayward, California. It is owned by Calvary Chapel of Hayward, Inc. ==History== KEPT-LP began broadcasting on February 14, 2015. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Organizations based in Hayward, California Category:2015 establishments in California EPT-LP EPT-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2015 EPT-LP
